{"tid":122091,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意音樂既入一入黎","createTime":"2017-02-15T18:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T09:00:43.000Z","uid":30390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"745f8fd61c284a5d5f765ee58300930ccb7124a9","tid":122091,"uid":30390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:21:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94-KCPOxd2Y&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D94-KCPOxd2Y%26feature%3Dshare&d=yztsqsfTIdfogAH81g8uWIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e2339948\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94-KCPOxd2Y&amp;feature=share</a><br />\n<br />\n夜闌人靜 無意睇到條高汁既演出<br />\n不禁令我體內對音樂既火出番黎<br />\n令我回想起中學既時候同一班同學<br />\n一齊夾band學結他   一齊參加音樂比賽<br />\n當自己有進步既時候既果份喜悅真係到依家都記得<br />\n<br />\n到我依家想再學翻樂器既時候、已經再無乜時間<br />\n金錢去做依件事<br />\n<br />\n純粹想分享下咁好既音樂同心路歷程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3352df3d76b4f6c374034fa831a1e8e5b58eaa7","tid":122091,"uid":2003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"真係幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e771dea1f260d009ea95a1723a074405d0ccb810","tid":122091,"uid":2966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T23:43:50.000Z","msg":"音樂真係可以救人"},{"pid":"9c425708e0c92a503b5c235a3ed895c62e0bbdef","tid":122091,"uid":30390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>音樂真係可以救人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01224bb9b083889f30d56ea6c06dba9edc628d59","tid":122091,"uid":8345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0a64c1d35eb29bf38de02d4060c8905e43dd9bd","tid":122091,"uid":30390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前